description: [``botocore``] Update cloudwatch client to latest version

[``botocore``] This release adds a new field (FlywheelArn) to the EntitiesDetectionJobProperties object. The FlywheelArn field is returned in the DescribeEntitiesDetectionJob and ListEntitiesDetectionJobs responses when the EntitiesDetection job is started with a FlywheelArn instead of an EntityRecognizerArn .
[``botocore``] Added error code CreateCustomDBEngineVersionFault for when the create custom engine version for Custom engines fails.
